## API

### Props

| Prop | Type | Default | Description |
|------|------|---------|------|
| `minItemWidth` | `string` | `'300px'` | Description for minItemWidth. |
| `gap` | `string` | `'1.5rem'` | Description for gap. |
| `maxColumns` | `number` | `4` | Description for maxColumns. |
| `interactive` | `boolean` | `true` | Description for interactive. |

## Notes

- Add class `tx-grid-layout__item` to items to enable hover styles.
